The project will be located along Ngumbi Road in Kisumu.The project will see the construction of 714 two-bedroom housing units. Kisumu Governor Anyang' Nyong’o’s ambitious plan for affordable housing has taken off with the launch on Wednesday of 1,200 housing units under the Sh3.8 billion Anderson Ofafa housing project.
Prof Nyong’o was joined by the Nation Media Group CEO Stephen Gitagama at the unveiling of the ambitious housing plan.



